"1 cup reduced-fat mayonnaise","1/2 cup loosely packed, shredded basil leaves","2 tablespoons chopped fresh parsley","1 tablespoon chopped fresh thyme","  Salt and pepper","24  slices white sandwich bread, toasted","1 pound thinly sliced roast turkey breast","1  large tomato, cut into 16 thin slices","16  strips bacon, cooked until crisp, cooled","8  large romaine lettuce leaves, cut in half widthwise"